cs.HC, cs.CR, cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.CC 

The paper focuses on improving the usability of fall-back authentication, which is a subfield of computer security (cs.CR). The proposed game design uses principles of human-computer interaction (cs.HC) to aid memorability and involves the use of persuasive technology (cs.CY). The game design also involves the use of graphical cues (cs.SI) and interactivity (cs.CC) to engage users and improve their ability to remember security questions.
